translated: Åstradsson, Johan Otto, battalion veterinarian, district veterinarian, Rockneby, b. 23/5/99 in Rödinge, Malmöh. 1st marriage 27, with Lisa Hallström. Children: Lans Ove b. 28, Anna-Lisa b. 29, Nils Bertil b. 32. — Secondary school: Ystad 17, veterinary school: 24. Battalion veterinarian in FVK reserve: 27, district veterinarian in Rockneby district: 34. Awarded the 4th Class Medal of the Royal Swedish Society of Military Sciences (FFrK4kl m^ isv.).
